pan> rapidly take steps</span><span style="font-size: 6.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt;"> -- including re-evaluating U.S. war plans -- </span><span class="UnderlineChar">to <span style="background: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow;">dampen the risks of</span> nuclear <span style="background: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow;">escalation</span> if conventional war erupts</span><span style="font-size: 6.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt;">. </span>

